</li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0045@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0046@@</p></li></ul></li></ol><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0047@@</p><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"h_4cc8ab562a\">@@body:0048@@</h1><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0049@@</p><ul><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0050@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0051@@</p><ul><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0052@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0053@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0054@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0055@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0056@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0057@@</p></li></ul></li></ul><h1 id=\"h_560d40fd69\">@@body:0058@@</h1><ul><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0059@@</p></li></ul><div class=\"intercom-container\"><img src=\"https://govocal---eu.intercom-attachments.eu/i/o/nfttr45j/90373910/ef0ea7f45ae5f192dad583fd5be7/image-3.png-expires%3D1768395600-req%3DdSgmEs19noJZWfMW1HO4zTod-2BkBSO2-2BB0h4O04m2n0eftZeKjyyjqVe8BSAE-0AnPYj-0A-signature%3Dc5757d4509ee2b1f6457377ab8735013e58ca64e404378d853e7e0f0b4dd9977?expires=1781870400&amp;signature=bdf7102a04ded2beecc6918f85e1acbfed48d8927b1f24fc50f03b22fd34845b&amp;req=2dVswlvzrTdk2hj99dpg6ktAmSdcGRv%2FIOOCRcI2hVan%2FWuDBJd8fEQROP5%2B%0AN0iLPUZi9gk0zNkdRbWv3uat%0A\"/></div><ul><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0060@@</p></li></ul><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0061@@</p><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"h_59025ad037\">@@body:0062@@</h1><ol><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0063@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0064@@</p></li></ol><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"h_7a5fe61cb6\">@@body:0065@@</h1><ul><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0066@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0067@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0068@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0069@@</p></li></ul>",
  "segments": {
    "title": {
      "field": "title",
      "text": "Setting up an online workshop",
      "hash": "174f0c790412"
    },
    "description": {
      "field": "description",
      "text": "We'll guide you through the key steps of setting up your own online workshops.",
      "hash": "4f53ac61edb2"
    },
    "body:0001": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "What are online workshops?",
      "hash": "bfb49a4c88f9"
    },
    "body:0002": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "The Online Workshop feature enables admins to host live, interactive sessions on the platform, including breakout groups, polls, Q&amp;A, and real-time collaboration.",
      "hash": "8bbbfac95dc3"
    },
    "body:0003": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Supports up to 50 participants",
      "hash": "70ee9b91c2ff"
    },
    "body:0004": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Works on desktop only (Chrome, Firefox, Edge)",
      "hash": "931efc04004b"
    },
    "body:0005": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Allows for multi-step agendas and data exports",
      "hash": "b369240cdd08"
    },
    "body:0006": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "What are the different room steps?",
      "hash": "9d5f0cd1d74f"
    },
    "body:0007": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Workshops support several participation methods within each room-step. Each method determines how participants interact in that step and what appears on the right side of the screen (the video feed always remains on the left).",
      "hash": "bd7eeca3f649"
    },
    "body:0008": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Q&amp;A",
      "hash": "b8b61fa19ebb"
    },
    "body:0009": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Allows admins to ask questions and participants to post answers (up to 255 characters) or vote on others’ responses",
      "hash": "770b7a3762cd"
    },
    "body:0010": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Posts can be shown as square cards or rectangular list items",
      "hash": "c68d64f1f9c8"
    },
    "body:0011": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Optional setting: Select <b>Copy Q&amp;A inputs from previous step</b> to carry over discussion points between steps",
      "hash": "f947155f1541"
    },
    "body:0012": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Info",
      "hash": "170322a32f3c"
    },
    "body:0013": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Displays text, images, or embedded media",
      "hash": "c6024d37ba3f"
    },
    "body:0014": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Useful for sharing instructions, context, or presentations",
      "hash": "169fb93e0641"
    },
    "body:0015": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Allows screen sharing and a “Full screen for all” option for better visibility during presentations",
      "hash": "5dbc5b981927"
    },
    "body:0016": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Breakout Rooms",
      "hash": "3df2db398dbd"
    },
    "body:0017": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Moves participants into smaller discussion groups",
      "hash": "0ec78b33272a"
    },
    "body:0018": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Options:",
      "hash": "367431fd664b"
    },
    "body:0019": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Self-selection (participants choose their room)",
      "hash": "6039b2f699e1"
    },
    "body:0020": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Random assignment (admin distributes them evenly)",
      "hash": "ccdef98dde64"
    },
    "body:0021": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Room configurations can be shared across multiple breakout rooms for easier management",
      "hash": "445e00e603e5"
    },
    "body:0022": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Don't forget! You will need to configure each of the smaller break out rooms with their own participation method.",
      "hash": "1fa1792fd518"
    },
    "body:0023": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Summarise Discussion",
      "hash": "e6d500345f2a"
    },
    "body:0024": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Used at the end of breakout discussions to collaboratively draft a summary",
      "hash": "c60bf0fcfaf8"
    },
    "body:0025": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "All participants in that room can type/edit the shared text",
      "hash": "cb8900141c08"
    },
    "body:0026": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Report Out",
      "hash": "495a1071178f"
    },
    "body:0027": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Used in the plenary room to show all breakout room summaries at once.",
      "hash": "9e010ffa42f4"
    },
    "body:0028": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Allows the workshop to “bring everyone back together” and display consolidated conclusions.",
      "hash": "f795732916c1"
    },
    "body:0029": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How to create an online workshop?",
      "hash": "e87017752aa5"
    },
    "body:0030": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Go to <b>Online deliberation workshops</b> in the <b>Tools</b> section of the admin panel",
      "hash": "8da1a48b46ba"
    },
    "body:0031": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Click <b>Manage your workshops</b> → <b>+ Add workshop</b>",
      "hash": "3b6152ce9327"
    },
    "body:0032": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Enter a <b>name</b>, <b>date</b>, and <b>slug</b> (used for the workshop URL)",
      "hash": "fd97d2ae28ae"
    },
    "body:0033": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "The URL will follow the format: <a class=\"intercom-content-link\" href=\"http://yourplatform.govocal.com/workshops/slug\" target=\"_blank\">yourplatform.govocal.com/workshops/slug</a>",
      "hash": "d43bffdda2b2"
    },
    "body:0034": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How to define your workshop?",
      "hash": "4e7ae14a3ec6"
    },
    "body:0035": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Use the <b>Manage</b> panel → <b>+ Add step</b>",
      "hash": "f143b796fff3"
    },
    "body:0036": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Common steps: Welcome, discussion steps, breakout sessions, Conclusion",
      "hash": "6b23c0e2e692"
    },
    "body:0037": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Steps can be reordered later",
      "hash": "d6414df6e3cc"
    },
    "body:0038": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How to add rooms to your workshop?",
      "hash": "ec19247bd75f"
    },
    "body:0039": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Add rooms via <b>+ Add room</b>.",
      "hash": "ff532bfeb98e"
    },
    "body:0040": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Types:",
      "hash": "0be4fcf6f52f"
    },
    "body:0041": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Plenary room (all participants together)",
      "hash": "ef69800cf542"
    },
    "body:0042": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Breakout rooms (smaller groups, 5–8 people each recommended)",
      "hash": "8c93d0e3c7de"
    },
    "body:0043": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Configure video/chat options:",
      "hash": "d1568b51b82b"
    },
    "body:0044": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Raise hand",
      "hash": "fdde0eba3c59"
    },
    "body:0045": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Microphone/camera on/off by default",
      "hash": "030f387a0bc1"
    },
    "body:0046": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Screen sharing",
      "hash": "74dc20e1c6c9"
    },
    "body:0047": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "ℹ️ : Admins always have full rights regardless of room settings.",
      "hash": "ded3ee769d4e"
    },
    "body:0048": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How to configure room steps?",
      "hash": "a123446121e3"
    },
    "body:0049": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Each room-step defines what happens in which room during each step.",
      "hash": "349db855c01d"
    },
    "body:0050": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Hover at the <b>step/room intersection</b> → <b>+ Add roomstep</b>",
      "hash": "91cb36d90381"
    },
    "body:0051": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Choose a participation method:",
      "hash": "8caf302381d3"
    },
    "body:0052": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Q&amp;A</b> → Post or vote on answers.",
      "hash": "57097be82c74"
    },
    "body:0053": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Poll</b> → Single/multiple choice questions.",
      "hash": "c778ccd5a86e"
    },
    "body:0054": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Info</b> → Share text/images, enable screen sharing.",
      "hash": "e47d1c2c9e2a"
    },
    "body:0055": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Breakout rooms</b> → Self-select or random assignment.",
      "hash": "ca9ba7314c7a"
    },
    "body:0056": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Summarise discussion</b> → Collaboratively draft conclusions.",
      "hash": "16b9830997c0"
    },
    "body:0057": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Report out</b> → Display summaries from all breakout rooms.",
      "hash": "34d867807b0f"
    },
    "body:0058": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How to test and edit the workshop?",
      "hash": "cd81d28194f8"
    },
    "body:0059": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Use <b>Next step</b> button or <b>timer</b> (10s, 1min, 5min countdown).",
      "hash": "568c6836ec6f"
    },
    "body:0060": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Steps can be <b>reordered</b> in the Manage panel.",
      "hash": "572940426fb3"
    },
    "body:0061": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "⚠️ : <i>Do not add “test” written input, it can’t be deleted easily without redoing the roomstep.</i>",
      "hash": "3788989156d0"
    },
    "body:0062": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How to export workshop data?",
      "hash": "73e8de3ea1bc"
    },
    "body:0063": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Admin panel → <b>Export Data</b>",
      "hash": "2b9246a23c1c"
    },
    "body:0064": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Downloads Excel file with a <b>tab per step</b> (polls, Q&amp;A, conclusions)",
      "hash": "a9088721668d"
    },
    "body:0065": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Workshop capacity and browser rules",
      "hash": "7aaf795caac4"
    },
    "body:0066": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Max 50 participants",
      "hash": "72cbef1b48c5"
    },
    "body:0067": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Desktop only (no mobile/tablet)",
      "hash": "d87416062ff3"
    },
    "body:0068": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Chrome, Firefox, or Edge required",
      "hash": "9e2939165ab6"
    },
    "body:0069": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "For company laptops: may require IT support for network settings",
      "hash": "3369c0626589"
    }
  }
}